name: A walk
description:
| A series of Happening taking place in the streets of Tunis |

المشية consists of a walk around the streets of Tunis whilst being chained to heterogeneous randomly picked objects, the experience was shared with a random audience crossed on the way.
Urban waste, e-waste, materials, all kinds of debris from our daily life ... Stuff we pass by everyday, but we barely pay attention to. All assembled and dragged by the body until it's breathless.
